Program: Outlook
Title: 25/04/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00g3t8c
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 26 Apr 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, a British family's agonising decision to end the life of a precious son five years after a accident left him in a persistent vegetative state. We hear from Christopher's mother Helen Watson and his identical twin brother Andrew who survived the same car crash with only minor injuries. Show less